This card gains corresponding effects if you Normal Summon it by Tributing these monsters.● Green Gadget: This card gains 300 ATK.● Red Gadget: When this card inflicts battle damage to your opponent by a direct attack: Inflict 500 damage to your opponent.● Yellow Gadget: If this card destroys an opponent's monster by battle: Inflict 700 damage to your opponent.
